description: Lists the available namespaces within a resourceGroup.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group. If resourceGroupName value is null the method lists all the namespaces within subscription

subscription_id.description: Gets subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

nextlink.description: Link to the next set of results. Not empty if Value contains incomplete list of Namespaces

value.description: Result of the List Namespace operation.
